---
const personalImageAlt = "Javier Gonzalez Soldado";
---

<article
    class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-12 text-primary md:flex-row md:gap-16 animate-fade-in"
>
    <!-- Animated background elements -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-primaryDark/10 rounded-full blur-xl animate-float"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/10 to-primaryDark/10 rounded-full blur-xl animate-float-delayed"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div
        class="[&>p]:mb-6 [&>p>strong]:text-transparent [&>p>strong]:text-secondary [&>p>strong]:font-medium [&>p>strong]:font-mono
        text-pretty order-2 md:order-1 max-w-3xl animate-slide-in-left"
    >
        <p
            class="opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up"
            style="animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
        >
            Me llamo <strong>Javier</strong>. Me introduje en la programación
            mediante la robótica educativa, tenía 14 años. Actualmente soy
            <strong>ingeniero telemático</strong> con un
            <strong>Máster</strong> de <strong>Desarrollo de Software</strong>.
            Poseo experiencia en el sector de la <strong>IA Generativa</strong>
            y el <strong>Desarrollo de Software</strong>.
        </p>

        <p
            class="opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up"
            style="animation-delay: 0.4s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
        >
            Algunos de mis éxitos incluyen <strong
                >Dos premios extraordinarios</strong
            >
            tanto en el Master como en el Grado. También he colaborado en varios
            proyectos de investigación, destacando mi trabajo fin de carrera en el
            que obtuve una calificación de <strong>10-MH</strong> y en el cual trabajé
            con el software real de la misión espacial <strong
                >Solar Orbiter</strong
            >
        </p>

        <p
            class="opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up"
            style="animation-delay: 0.6s; animation-fill-mode: forwards;"
        >
            Personalmente, me fascina el <strong>conocimiento</strong> y siempre
            intento estar <strong>actualizado</strong> leyendo libros o artículos.
            Constantemente estoy mejorando mis conocimientos y habilidades para ser
            un <strong>desarrollador de software</strong> de calidad.
        </p>

        <!-- Animated accent line -->
        <div
            class="w-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primaryDark rounded-full mt-8 animate-expand-width"
            style="animation-delay: 0.8s;"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative group order-1 md:order-2 animate-slide-in-right">
        <!-- Animated ring background -->
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/90 to-primaryDark/90 rounded-2xl blur-lg
            scale-110 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-500 animate-pulse-subtle"
        >
        </div>

        <!-- Image container with advanced styling -->
        <div
            class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primaryDark/10
            p-1 backdrop-blur-sm ring-1 ring-black/10 dark:ring-white/10 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105
            hover:rotate-1 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/25"
        >
            <img
                width="200"
                height="200"
                src="aboutme.webp"
                alt={personalImageAlt}
                class="object-cover w-64 h-64 rounded-xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-110 group-hover:brightness-110"
                style="object-position: 50% 50%"
            />

            <!-- Overlay gradient on hover -->
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/20 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 rounded-xl"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating elements around image -->
        <div
            class="absolute -top-2 -left-2 w-4 h-4 bg-secondary rounded-full animate-bounce"
            style="animation-delay: 1s;"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-3 h-3 bg-secondary rounded-full animate-bounce"
            style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/2 -right-4 w-2 h-2 bg-secondary rounded-full animate-pulse"
            style="animation-delay: 2s;"
        >
        </div>
    </div>
</article>

<style>
    @keyframes fade-in {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes fade-in-up {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes slide-in-left {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-50px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes slide-in-right {
        from {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(50px);
        }
        to {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(0);
        }
    }

    @keyframes float {
        0%,
        100% {
            transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(180deg);
        }
    }

    @keyframes float-delayed {
        0%,
        100% {
            transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
        }
        50% {
            transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(-180deg);
        }
    }

    @keyframes expand-width {
        from {
            width: 0;
        }
        to {
            width: 100px;
        }
    }

    @keyframes pulse-subtle {
        0%,
        100% {
            opacity: 0.1;
        }
        50% {
            opacity: 0.3;
        }
    }

    .animate-fade-in {
        animation: fade-in 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-fade-in-up {
        animation: fade-in-up 0.6s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-slide-in-left {
        animation: slide-in-left 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-slide-in-right {
        animation: slide-in-right 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    .animate-float {
        animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .animate-float-delayed {
        animation: float-delayed 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .animate-expand-width {
        animation: expand-width 1s ease-out forwards;
    }

    .animate-pulse-subtle {
        animation: pulse-subtle 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    /* Ensure animations work on page load */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
        article {
            animation-duration: 0.8s;
            animation-timing-function: ease-out;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }
    }

    /* Respect user's motion preferences */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        * {
            animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;
            animation-iteration-count: 1 !important;
            transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;
        }
    }
</style>
